com.google.api.gax.grpc

Class ApiCallSettings.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.gax.grpc.ApiCallSettings.Builder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    com.google.api.gax.grpc.ApiCallSettingsTyped.Builder
    Enclosing class:
    ApiCallSettings

    public static class ApiCallSettings.Builder
extends Object
    A base builder class for ApiCallSettings. This class cannot be used to create an instance of the abstract base class ApiCallSettings. See the class documentation of ApiCallSettings for a description of the different values that can be set, and for a description of when this builder may be used. Builders for concrete derived classes such as SimpleCallSettings, PageStreamingCallSettings, or BundlingCallSettings can be used to create instances of those classes.
